summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Tilo Live website. All backend APIs (11/11) and frontend functionality working perfectly. Admin panel, contact forms, newsletter signup, navigation, and mobile responsiveness all functional.

Home page loads with hero section, features, CTA buttons
Salary page displays host tiers (Bronze to Diamond) and agent commission structure

Admin dashboard all tabs functional (Dashboard, Settings, Messages, Newsletters, Compose, SMTP)
WhatsApp float button present and functional
Mobile responsive design with working mobile menu
